overview: The annual Student Body President election at wildly eclectic and diverse West Beach High pits the quirky, much-beloved incumbent Sissy Frenchfry against handsome, charismatic -- and socially intolerant -- transfer student Bodey McDodey, who enacts a devious plan to restore the "status quo."
tagline: Hey, I haven't met you yet. I'm Sissy Frenchfry!
title: Sissy Frenchfry
